data.description: Welcome to your new home in the charming neighborhood of Old Aurora! This delightful residence offers ample space & a host of fantastic features that are sure to impress. Step inside & discover generously sized bedrooms, each complete with its own walk-in closet, providing plenty of storage & organization options. Hall bath boasts double vanities, ensuring convenience for all family members, while the master bath offers a single vanity with ample countertop space, perfect for your morning routines. Throughout the home, you'll find new laminate wood flooring in the formal living & dining areas, as well as in all the bedrooms, giving the home a fresh and modern look. New travertine tiles grace the kitchen, breakfast area, bathrooms, and den, adding an elegant touch to these spaces. The kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring stainless steel appliances, new cabinets with beautiful quartz countertops that offer both style & functionality. This home also comes with a detached garage, providing secure parking & extra storage space for your belongings. The covered patio is the perfect spot to unwind and enjoy the outdoors, whether you're sipping your morning coffee or hosting a barbecue with friends and family. Rest assured that the HVAC is only 6 months old and roof was replaced in 2018, offering peace of mind and protection for years to come. Located in the historic and sought-after Old Aurora neighborhood, this home offers a fantastic blend of character and modern amenities. This is a wonderful opportunity to own a piece of this vibrant community. Schedule a showing today and make this house your home!
